Farvel.

70
00:12:12,413 --> 00:12:14,373
- Sam!
- Jeg fandt det lige.

71
00:12:14,499 --> 00:12:16,584
Sam, læg det fra dig!

72
00:12:16,709 --> 00:12:18,544
- Louisa...
- Far!

73
